name: Vessels 050: Le Fay Woods Witch
description: Witchcraft is a central motif of the Vessel story.  Strange latent powers come to bear at moments of stress or danger.  The establisment does not like witchcraft at all.  The witches are hunted and killed if discovered.  This card is an edition of 50 priced at 5 tezos instead of a 1/1 (25, 50, 75 and 100) all follow this pattern.
